OL,5, Three foreign-born residents in Japan  
OL,6, have sued the country's authorities    
OL,7, over alleged racial profiling.         
OL,9,FThe plaintiffs say they have suffered  
OL,10,Fdistress from repeated police          
OL,11,Fquestioning based on their appearances.
OL,13,F"There's a very strong image that      
OL,14,F'foreigner' equals 'criminal',"        
OL,15,FPakistan-born Syed Zain told reporters.
OL,17,FThe lawsuit filed on Monday aims to    
OL,18,Fconfirm that racial profiling is       
OL,19,Fillegal and to seek 3m yen ($20,250;   
OL,20,F#15,740) in damages for each plaintiff.
